<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l3">von der nom <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / als Jr bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſchade<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyt etc / Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l5">wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd alſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache 
<add><ab facs="#facs_182_r1l4">gen eẅch </ab></add> / Vns vmb <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l6">wandel / vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein <expan>keru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> ʒutun / bey <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Marſchalk Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l8">bey <expan>dyecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Marſchalk <expan>ſeın<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan>
