<ab facs="#facs_182_r1l9">Marſchalk <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıben</expan> daʒ ſıe ſıch des <expan>v<ex>er</ex>fahen</expan> vnd <expan>auſſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
