</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_182" id="90r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Görgen von Gawberstat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst bevor. Görg von Gawberstat, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der nom
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als ir bey
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>schade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> seyt etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und also
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        sache <add>gen ewch</add> uns umb <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> wandel und
                        den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein <expan>keru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> zu tun
                        bey <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Marschalk und bey
                            <expan>Dyecze<ex>n</ex></expan> Marschalk <expan>sein<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan>, <add>in der frewntlikeit</add> auch
                        beleiben, ob uns <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> zwen Marschalk
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreiben</expan>, daz sie sich des
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>fahen</expan> und
                            <expan>ausspreche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> und daz uns des
                            <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">sand Merteins tag</q>11.11.1420</note>
</app> schierist ein ausztrag <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
